---
const pulseBeats = [
  {
    n: "01",
    name: "Gratitude",
    desc: "Dreamy, calm establishing shots before the rush — landscape, architecture, the location waking up.",
  },
  {
    n: "02",
    name: "Arrivals",
    desc: "Early-morning movement — breezy, flowing Pilates and yoga moments, the bath always present in frame.",
  },
  {
    n: "03",
    name: "Setting an intention",
    desc: "Intimate, loose, warming up — leaning against the bath, waiting, waking into the day.",
  },
  {
    n: "04",
    name: "Finding fire",
    desc: "Intensity. Flushed cheeks, sweat, quick cuts — fully in the moment, the bath waiting in the background.",
  },
  {
    n: "05",
    name: "Committing — the plunge",
    desc: "The hero beat. The breath before you go for it: hesitation, resolve, elation — the product's moment of truth.",
  },
  {
    n: "06",
    name: "Mastery",
    desc: "A wide, centered exhale after the cold — symmetry, clear horizons, a new state of mind.",
  },
  {
    n: "07",
    name: "Product moments",
    desc: "Tight, tactile detail — toe to water, hands on the teak edge, grain and shadow — the craftsmanship up close.",
  },
];
---

<section class="container py-[40px] md:py-[64px]">
  {/* Intro */}
  <div class="grid gap-y-[24px] md:grid-cols-12 md:gap-x-[40px]">
    <h2
      class="md:col-span-3 font-neue-montreal-mono text-[14px] font-light uppercase triangle-after-right text-[#919191]"
      data-reveal
    >
      Art Direction
    </h2>
    <div class="flex flex-col gap-[24px] md:col-span-8 md:col-start-5" data-reveal>
      <h3 class="font-neue-montreal font-medium text-[22px] md:text-[28px] leading-[1.2] text-white">
        Directing the campaign that made it feel premium
      </h3>
      <p class="font-neue-montreal text-[18px] md:text-[22px] leading-[1.5] text-white/80">
        A cold plunge is a tub of cold water until the imagery tells you otherwise.
        To give icebaths.com a world worth paying a premium for, I produced and
        art-directed a full lifestyle photo and video campaign — writing the
        concept, building the shot list, and directing the crew on set across a Bali
        location.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div
      class="md:col-span-8 md:col-start-5 grid grid-cols-3 gap-[8px] md:gap-[12px]"
      data-reveal
    >
      <img
        src="/icebaths/art-1.jpg"
        alt="icebaths.com lifestyle campaign still"
        loading="lazy"
        decoding="async"
        class="aspect-[4/5] w-full rounded-[8px] object-cover"
      />
      <img
        src="/icebaths/art-2.jpg"
        alt="icebaths.com lifestyle campaign still"
        loading="lazy"
        decoding="async"
        class="aspect-[4/5] w-full rounded-[8px] object-cover"
      />
      <img
        src="/icebaths/art-3.jpg"
        alt="icebaths.com lifestyle campaign still"
        loading="lazy"
        decoding="async"
        class="aspect-[4/5] w-full rounded-[8px] object-cover"
      />
    </div>
  </div>

  {/* Campaign Concept · Pulse — 50/50 split-panel card */}
  <div class="mt-[64px] md:mt-[96px]" data-reveal>
    <div class="grid overflow-hidden rounded-[16px] border border-white/15 md:grid-cols-2">
      <div class="flex flex-col justify-center gap-[14px] p-[24px] md:p-[36px]">
        <span class="font-neue-montreal-mono text-[14px] uppercase text-[#919191]">
          Campaign Concept · Pulse
        </span>
        <h3 class="font-pp-seiko uppercase leading-[0.95] text-[32px] md:text-[44px] text-white">
          Pulse
        </h3>
        <p class="font-neue-montreal text-[15px] md:text-[17px] leading-[1.45] text-white/80">
          The idea behind the shoot: life moves fast enough that you can forget
          you're alive — and the cold plunge is the jolt that brings you back to
          the present.
        </p>
        <p class="font-neue-montreal text-[15px] md:text-[17px] leading-[1.45] text-white/80">
          I structured the campaign as a single emotional journey, from the quiet
          of early morning through the heat of a workout to the shock and clarity
          of the plunge — so every frame ladders up to one feeling rather than a
          pile of disconnected product shots.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="h-[240px] md:h-[420px]">
        <img
          src="/icebaths/campaign-pulse.jpg"
          alt="icebaths.com campaign hero — the cold plunge"
          loading="lazy"
          decoding="async"
          class="h-full w-full object-cover"
        />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  {/* The seven-beat emotional arc */}
  <div class="mt-[40px] md:mt-[64px] grid gap-y-[24px] md:grid-cols-12 md:gap-x-[40px]">
    <span
      class="md:col-span-3 font-neue-montreal-mono text-[14px] uppercase triangle-after-right text-[#919191]"
      data-reveal
    >
      The arc · seven beats
    </span>
    <ol class="flex flex-col md:col-span-8 md:col-start-5" data-reveal>
      {pulseBeats.map((beat) => (
        <li class="grid grid-cols-[auto_1fr] gap-x-[20px] md:gap-x-[32px] border-t border-white/15 py-[24px]">
          <span class="font-neue-montreal-mono text-[14px] text-[#919191]">
            {beat.n}
          </span>
          <div class="flex flex-col gap-[8px]">
            <h4 class="font-neue-montreal font-medium text-[20px] md:text-[24px] text-white">
              {beat.name}
            </h4>
            <p class="font-neue-montreal text-[16px] md:text-[18px] leading-[1.5] text-white/70">
              {beat.desc}
            </p>
          </div>
        </li>
      ))}
    </ol>
  </div>

  {/* Campaign film — Contra showcase */}
  <div class="mt-[64px] md:mt-[96px] grid gap-y-[24px] md:grid-cols-12 md:gap-x-[40px]">
    <span
      class="md:col-span-3 font-neue-montreal-mono text-[14px] uppercase triangle-after-right text-[#919191]"
      data-reveal
    >
      Campaign Film
    </span>
    <div class="md:col-span-8 md:col-start-5" data-reveal>
      <video
        class="w-full rounded-[16px] border border-white/15"
        controls
        playsinline
        preload="none"
        poster="https://media.contra.com/video/upload/fl_progressive/q_auto:best,w_2000/txv9isrns4n1ctxrrosa.webp"
      >
        <source
          src="https://media.contra.com/video/upload/fl_progressive/q_auto:best,w_2000/txv9isrns4n1ctxrrosa.mp4"
          type="video/mp4"
        />
        <a
          href="https://contra.com/p/PmZWRlov-icebathscom-art-director-lifestyle-shoot-video-shoot?r=samuel_tirtawidjaja"
        >
          Watch the campaign film on Contra
        </a>
      </video>
    </div>
  </div>

  {/* The same process · 3D product imagery */}
  <div class="mt-[64px] md:mt-[96px] grid gap-y-[24px] md:grid-cols-12 md:gap-x-[40px]">
    <span
      class="md:col-span-3 font-neue-montreal-mono text-[14px] uppercase triangle-after-right text-[#919191]"
      data-reveal
    >
      The same process · 3D product imagery
    </span>
    <div class="flex flex-col gap-[24px] md:col-span-8 md:col-start-5" data-reveal>
      <h3 class="font-neue-montreal font-medium text-[22px] md:text-[28px] leading-[1.2] text-white">
        I direct 3D renders the same way I direct a shoot
      </h3>
      <p class="font-neue-montreal text-[18px] md:text-[22px] leading-[1.5] text-white/80">
        Whether it's a film crew or a 3D pipeline, the job is the same: set the
        concept, define the mood and framing, then guide the people and tools
        through each shot until it matches the vision. I use this exact approach to
        produce the brand's 3D product imagery — scripting the camera moves,
        lighting, materials, and hero angles so the renders carry the same intention
        as the campaign, not just a spinning model on a grey background.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
